msgctxt "17256_松岡里緒奈：源氏名"
msgid "I played soccer when I was in junior high. I was pretty good, too. I could hold my own against the boys, you know."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "17268_Kiryu"
msgid "You were on the girls' soccer team, huh?"
msgstr "Estabas en el equipo de fútbol femenino, ¿eh?"

msgctxt "17280_松岡里緒奈：源氏名"
msgid "Oh, no. I got special permission to join the boys' team. I was a regular player, too."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "17292_Kiryu"
msgid "That's impressive."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "17304_松岡里緒奈：源氏名"
msgid "My dream was to play in the national championships in high school, but..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "17316_Kiryu"
msgid "But?"
msgstr "¿Pero?"

msgctxt "17328_松岡里緒奈：源氏名"
msgid "I had to quit before I got into high school. I had a... physical problem."
msgstr "Tuve que renunciar antes de entrar a la escuela secundaria. Tuve un... problema físico."

msgctxt "17340_Kiryu"
msgid "Were you injured?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "17352_松岡里緒奈：源氏名"
msgid "No... It was more of a handicap."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "17364_Kiryu"
msgid "Let me try to guess where the problem was."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "17376_松岡里緒奈：源氏名"
msgid "I don't usually wear many accessories on my days off, but I think I'll try something for a change."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "17388_Kiryu"
msgid "Sounds like a good idea to me."
msgstr "Parece una buena idea."

msgctxt "17400_松岡里緒奈：源氏名"
msgid "But I don't have enough money to buy many. If I wore an accessory on just one part of my body, where should it be?"
msgstr "Pero no tengo suficiente dinero para comprar muchos. Si llevara un accesorio en una sola parte del cuerpo, ¿dónde debería estar?"

msgctxt "17412_Kiryu"
msgid "Hmm..."
msgstr "Mmm..."

msgctxt "17448_松岡里緒奈：源氏名"
msgid "Look! This is the present you gave me!"
msgstr "¡Mire! ¡Este es el regalo que usted me dio!"

msgctxt "17460_Kiryu"
msgid "It looks great! I'll always treasure it. <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"
msgstr "¡Se ve genial! Siempre lo atesoraré. <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "17472_松岡里緒奈：源氏名"
msgid "I'm a little thirsty! Can I order a <Color:7>Beer?<Color:Default>"
msgstr "Tengo un poco de sed. ¿Puedo ordenar una <Color:7>Cerveza?<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "17484_松岡里緒奈：源氏名"
msgid "Yay! I'll order, then."
msgstr "¡Qué bien! Pediré una, entonces."

msgctxt "17496_F_cab_sitsofa_sync_order"
msgid "Excuse me!"
