msgctxt "17616_松岡里緒奈：源氏名"
msgid "I thought your email was hilarious! <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "17628_松岡里緒奈：源氏名"
msgid "I guess mine was a little hard to read, all bunched up like that, but most people would just ignore that."
